objects.description: [SLOTHFULMEDIA](https://attack.mitre.org/software/S0533) has deleted itself and the 'index.dat' file on a compromised machine to remove recent Internet history from the system.(Citation: CISA MAR SLOTHFULMEDIA October 2020)

external_references.description: DHS/CISA, Cyber National Mission Force. (2020, October 1). Malware Analysis Report (MAR) MAR-10303705-1.v1 – Remote Access Trojan: SLOTHFULMEDIA. Retrieved October 2, 2020.
